---
const title = "Casa de la Grana · Centro cultural";
const description = "Centro cultural dedicado a la preservación de la grana cochinilla y su significado histórico. Naturaleza, historia y cultura en Oaxaca.";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{title}</title>
  <meta name="description" content={description} />
  <meta property="og:title" content={title} />
  <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
  <meta property="og:image" content="/images/img-05.jpg" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/images/favicon.svg" />
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/images/apple-touch-icon.png" />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#a31300" />
  <style>
    /* ---- FONTS ---- */
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'ChivoMono';
      src: url('/fonts/ChivoMono-VariableFont_wght.ttf') format('truetype');
      font-weight: 100 900;
      font-style: normal;
      font-display: swap;
    }
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Chivo';
      src: url('/fonts/Chivo-VariableFont_wght.ttf') format('truetype');
      font-weight: 100 900;
      font-style: normal;
      font-display: swap;
    }
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Chivo';
      src: url('/fonts/Chivo-Italic-VariableFont_wght.ttf') format('truetype');
      font-weight: 100 900;
      font-style: italic;
      font-display: swap;
    }
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Koper';
      src: url('/fonts/Koper-Regular.otf') format('opentype');
      font-weight: 400;
      font-style: normal;
      font-display: swap;
    }

    /* ---- TOKENS ---- */
    :root {
      --surface-cream:   #f7f3f0;
      --surface-black:   #000000;
      --surface-grana:   #a31300;
      --text-dark:       #231c1a;
      --text-light:      #f7f3f0;
      --text-grana:      #a31300;
      --text-muted:      rgba(35,28,26,0.45);
      --text-muted-inv:  rgba(247,243,240,0.45);

      --font-mono:    'ChivoMono', monospace;
      --font-sans:    'Chivo', sans-serif;
      --font-serif:   'Koper', serif;

      --w-heavy:  900;
      --w-base:   300;
      --w-medium: 400;

      --space-xs:  8px;
      --space-sm:  16px;
      --space-md:  24px;
      --space-lg:  40px;
      --space-xl:  80px;
      --space-2xl: 120px;

      --radius-pill: 9999px;
      --radius-sm:   4px;

      --ease: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
      --dur:  400ms;
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      *, *::before, *::after {
        transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
        animation-duration:  0.01ms !important;
      }
    }

    /* ---- RESET ---- */
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: auto; }
    body {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-base);
      background: var(--surface-cream);
      color: var(--text-dark);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    img { display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; }
    a   { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    /* ---- NAV ---- */
    .nav {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0 0 auto;
      z-index: 100;
      height: 56px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 var(--space-md);
      background: var(--surface-cream);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(35,28,26,0.05);
    }
    .nav-logo img {
      height: 22px;
      width: auto;
      display: block;
    }
    .nav-menu-btn {
      background: none;
      border: 0;
      padding: 6px 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-base);
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      transition: color var(--dur) var(--ease);
    }
    .nav-menu-btn:hover { color: var(--text-grana); }
    .nav-menu-btn .dot {
      width: 7px;
      height: 7px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--text-grana);
      display: inline-block;
      transition: transform var(--dur) var(--ease);
    }
    body.menu-open .nav-menu-btn .dot { transform: scale(1.6); }

    /* ---- MENU OVERLAY ---- */
    .menu-overlay {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 99;
      background: var(--surface-cream);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      opacity: 0;
      visibility: hidden;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity var(--dur) var(--ease), visibility 0s var(--dur);
    }
    .menu-overlay.open {
      opacity: 1;
      visibility: visible;
      pointer-events: auto;
      transition: opacity var(--dur) var(--ease), visibility 0s 0s;
    }
    .menu-list {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-sm);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .menu-item {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-base);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      display: inline-block;
      position: relative;
      transition: color var(--dur) var(--ease);
    }
    .menu-item::before { content: "("; }
    .menu-item::after  { content: ")"; }
    .menu-item::before,
    .menu-item::after {
      display: inline-block;
      transition: padding var(--dur) var(--ease);
    }
    .menu-item:hover::before { padding-right: 0.5em; }
    .menu-item:hover::after  { padding-left: 0.5em; }
    .menu-item:hover { color: var(--text-grana); }

    /* ---- HERO ---- */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100svh;
      background: #000;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding-top: 56px;
    }
    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 56px 0 0 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: calc(100% - 56px);
      object-fit: cover;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .hero-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      min-height: calc(100svh - 56px);
    }
    .hero-word {
      position: absolute;
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-weight: var(--w-medium);
      font-size: clamp(4.5rem, 13.5vw, 14rem);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      line-height: 0.9;
      color: var(--text-light);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .hero-word-l { top: var(--space-lg); left: -1.2vw; }
    .hero-word-r { bottom: var(--space-lg); right: -1.2vw; }
    .hero-tag {
      position: absolute;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-base);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-light);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .hero-tag-tr { top: calc(var(--space-lg) + 11.5vw); right: var(--space-lg); }
    .hero-tag-bl { bottom: calc(var(--space-lg) + 11.5vw); left: var(--space-lg); }

    /* ---- EXPOSITION ---- */
    .expo {
      background: var(--surface-black);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .expo-text {
      padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: var(--space-md);
    }
    .label {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-base);
      font-size: 9px;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-grana);
    }
    .label-inv {
      color: var(--text-muted-inv);
    }
    .expo-heading {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-heavy);
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      line-height: 1.0;
      color: var(--text-light);
    }
    .expo-body {
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--text-muted-inv);
      max-width: 40ch;
    }
    .expo-img {
      overflow: hidden;
      min-height: 480px;
    }
    .expo-img img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    /* ---- BUTTONS ---- */
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-xs);
      padding: 12px var(--space-md);
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-medium);
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      min-height: 44px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background var(--dur) var(--ease),
                  color var(--dur) var(--ease),
                  border-color var(--dur) var(--ease);
    }
    .btn-grana {
      background: var(--surface-grana);
      color: var(--text-light);
      border-color: var(--surface-grana);
    }
    .btn-grana:hover { background: #8a1000; border-color: #8a1000; }
    .btn-outline-light {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text-light);
      border-color: rgba(247,243,240,0.3);
    }
    .btn-outline-light:hover { background: var(--text-light); color: var(--text-dark); border-color: var(--text-light); }
    .btn-outline-dark {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      border-color: rgba(35,28,26,0.3);
    }
    .btn-outline-dark:hover { background: var(--text-dark); color: var(--text-light); border-color: var(--text-dark); }

    /* ---- MANIFESTO ---- */
    .manifesto {
      background: var(--surface-cream);
      padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
    }
    .manifesto-header {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
      align-items: start;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    }
    .manifesto-heading {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-heavy);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 4rem);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      line-height: 0.92;
      color: var(--text-grana);
    }
    .manifesto-body {
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      padding-top: var(--space-sm);
    }
    .manifesto-body p + p { margin-top: 1em; }
    .manifesto-imgs {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4px;
      height: 480px;
    }
    .manifesto-img {
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .manifesto-img img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform var(--dur) var(--ease);
    }
    .manifesto-img:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }

    /* ---- FAVORITOS ---- */
    .favoritos {
      background: var(--surface-cream);
      padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
    }
    .favoritos-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-sm);
    }
    .favoritos-word {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-heavy);
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5.5vw, 5rem);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      line-height: 0.9;
      color: var(--text-dark);
    }
    .favoritos-word.right {
      text-align: right;
    }
    .favoritos-cards {
      grid-column: span 2;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-sm);
    }
    .product-card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-xs);
    }
    .product-img {
      aspect-ratio: 3/4;
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      overflow: hidden;
      background: rgba(35,28,26,0.04);
    }
    .product-img img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform var(--dur) var(--ease);
    }
    .product-card:hover .product-img img { transform: scale(1.05); }
    .product-name {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-dark);
    }
    .product-detail {
      font-size: 9px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    /* ---- TINA Y AMIGOS ---- */
    .tina {
      background: var(--surface-cream);
    }
    .tina-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .tina-text {
      padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: var(--space-md);
    }
    .tina-heading {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-heavy);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.8rem);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      line-height: 0.9;
      color: var(--text-dark);
    }
    .tina-sub {
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 38ch;
    }
    .tina-imgs {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4px;
      min-height: 480px;
    }
    .tina-img {
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .tina-img:first-child {
      grid-row: span 2;
    }
    .tina-img img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform var(--dur) var(--ease);
    }
    .tina-img:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }

    /* ---- QUOTE ---- */
    .quote {
      background: var(--surface-black);
      padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .quote-text {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-weight: var(--w-medium);
      font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: var(--text-light);
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .quote-attr {
      display: block;
      margin-top: var(--space-md);
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-base);
      font-size: 9px;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-muted-inv);
    }

    /* ---- BRIDGE ---- */
    .bridge {
      background: var(--surface-black);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .bridge-text {
      padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-lg);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: var(--space-md);
    }
    .bridge-eyebrow { color: rgba(247,243,240,0.6); }
    .bridge-heading {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-weight: var(--w-medium);
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 7rem);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      line-height: 0.9;
      color: var(--text-light);
    }
    .bridge-body {
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text-muted-inv);
      max-width: 42ch;
    }
    .bridge-btns { display: flex; gap: var(--space-sm); flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: var(--space-md); }
    .btn-square-light {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text-light);
      border: 1px solid var(--text-light);
      border-radius: 0;
      padding: 10px 22px;
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      min-height: 36px;
    }
    .btn-square-light:hover { background: var(--text-light); color: var(--text-dark); }
    .bridge-img {
      overflow: hidden;
      min-height: 480px;
    }
    .bridge-img img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    /* ---- FOOTER ---- */
    footer {
      background: var(--surface-cream);
      padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-lg) var(--space-lg);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      align-items: start;
      gap: var(--space-lg);
    }
    .footer-col h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-base);
      font-size: 9px;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-grana);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }
    .footer-col p,
    .footer-col address,
    .footer-col a {
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-weight: 300;
      font-style: normal;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text-dark);
    }
    .footer-col a { display: block; }
    .footer-col a:hover { color: var(--text-grana); }
    .footer-bottom {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding-top: var(--space-2xl);
      margin-top: var(--space-lg);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(35,28,26,0.08);
    }
    .footer-bottom-logo img { height: 22px; width: auto; display: block; }
    .footer-copy {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-base);
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    /* ---- FLOATING NAV ---- */
    .float-nav {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: var(--space-md);
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      z-index: 98;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      background: rgba(247,243,240,0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(35,28,26,0.1);
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .float-nav a {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-base);
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      padding: 14px 18px;
      min-height: 44px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      transition: color var(--dur) var(--ease);
    }
    .float-nav a:hover { color: var(--text-grana); }
    .float-nav a:first-child { border-radius: var(--radius-pill) 0 0 var(--radius-pill); }
    .float-nav a:last-child  { border-radius: 0 var(--radius-pill) var(--radius-pill) 0; }

    /* ---- INTRO / BIENVENIDA ---- */
    .intro {
      position: relative;
      background: var(--surface-cream);
      min-height: 92vh;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 60% 40%;
      align-items: center;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
    }
    .intro-blob {
      position: relative;
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .intro-blob img {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: none;
      height: auto;
      max-height: 78vh;
      object-fit: contain;
      object-position: left center;
      margin-left: -8%;
      display: block;
    }
    .intro-content {
      padding: 0 var(--space-lg) 0 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-2xl);
      align-items: stretch;
    }
    .intro-heading {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-weight: var(--w-medium);
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4.2vw, 4rem);
      line-height: 1.0;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      letter-spacing: -0.005em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .intro-secondary {
      align-self: flex-end;
      max-width: 320px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-sm);
    }
    .intro-body {
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: var(--text-dark);
    }
    .intro-secondary .btn {
      margin-top: var(--space-sm);
      align-self: flex-start;
    }
    .btn-square {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text-grana);
      border: 1px solid var(--text-grana);
      border-radius: 0;
      padding: 10px 22px;
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      min-height: 36px;
    }
    .btn-square:hover {
      background: var(--text-grana);
      color: var(--text-light);
    }

    /* ---- SHARED ---- */
    .eyebrow {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-base);
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-grana);
    }

    /* ---- PROYECTO ---- */
    .proyecto {
      background: var(--surface-cream);
      padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-lg);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto;
      gap: var(--space-lg);
      min-height: 90vh;
    }
    .proyecto-eyebrow {
      grid-column: 1 / 2;
      grid-row: 1;
      align-self: start;
    }
    .proyecto-title {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      grid-row: 2;
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-weight: var(--w-medium);
      font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 11vw, 11rem);
      line-height: 0.88;
      letter-spacing: -0.015em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-top: var(--space-md);
    }
    .proyecto-body {
      grid-column: 2 / 3;
      grid-row: 3;
      justify-self: end;
      max-width: 46ch;
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    }
    .proyecto-body p + p { margin-top: 1.2em; }
    .proyecto-body em { font-style: italic; color: var(--text-grana); }

    /* ---- GRANA / NOCHEZTLICALLI ---- */
    .grana {
      background: var(--surface-cream);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 5fr 7fr;
      gap: 0;
      min-height: 92vh;
    }
    .grana-img {
      overflow: hidden;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .grana-img img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center;
      display: block;
    }
    .grana-img img:first-child { object-position: center 40%; }
    .grana-img img:last-child  { object-position: center 60%; }
    .grana-content {
      padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-lg);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-lg);
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .grana-eyebrow {
      align-self: flex-start;
    }
    .grana-title {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-weight: var(--w-medium);
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 6.5rem);
      line-height: 0.9;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-dark);
    }
    .cedula {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 110px 1fr;
      column-gap: var(--space-md);
      row-gap: var(--space-sm);
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      line-height: 1.5;
      padding: var(--space-md) 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(35,28,26,0.15);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(35,28,26,0.15);
      max-width: 480px;
    }
    .cedula dt {
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      color: var(--text-grana);
      font-size: 9px;
      align-self: center;
    }
    .cedula dd { color: var(--text-dark); margin: 0; }
    .cedula dd em { font-style: italic; }
    .grana-body {
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      max-width: 50ch;
    }
    .grana-body p + p { margin-top: 1.1em; }

    /* ---- SISTEMA VISUAL ---- */
    .sistema {
      background: var(--surface-cream);
      padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-lg);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-lg);
    }
    .sistema-eyebrow { grid-column: 1; }
    .sistema-title {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-weight: var(--w-medium);
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 8rem);
      line-height: 0.92;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-top: var(--space-md);
    }
    .sistema-body {
      grid-column: 2;
      align-self: end;
      max-width: 46ch;
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-top: var(--space-md);
    }

    .module {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 4fr;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
      padding-top: var(--space-xl);
      align-items: start;
    }
    .module-label {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-base);
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-grana);
    }

    /* Paleta */
    .paleta {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
      gap: 4px;
    }
    .paleta-chip {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .paleta-swatch {
      aspect-ratio: 1;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .paleta-info {
      padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-xs) 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }
    .paleta-name {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-base);
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-dark);
    }
    .paleta-hex {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-base);
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    /* Tipografía */
    .tipos {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: var(--space-lg);
    }
    .tipo {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-md);
      padding: var(--space-lg) 0;
    }
    .tipo-spec {
      font-size: clamp(5rem, 9vw, 9rem);
      line-height: 0.85;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .tipo-koper { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-weight: var(--w-medium); text-transform: uppercase; }
    .tipo-mono  { font-family: var(--font-mono);  font-weight: var(--w-base); }
    .tipo-sans  { font-family: var(--font-sans);  font-weight: 300; }
    .tipo-meta {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-base);
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 4px;
    }
    .tipo-meta span { color: var(--text-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; }

    /* ---- PHOTO BREAK ---- */
    .photo-break {
      width: 100%;
      height: 72vh;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .photo-break img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center 30%;
      display: block;
    }

    /* ---- APLICACIONES ---- */
    .aplicaciones {
      background: var(--surface-cream);
      padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-lg);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-lg);
    }
    .aplicaciones-eyebrow { grid-column: 1; }
    .aplicaciones-title {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-weight: var(--w-medium);
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 8rem);
      line-height: 0.92;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-top: var(--space-md);
    }
    .aplicaciones-body {
      grid-column: 2;
      align-self: end;
      max-width: 46ch;
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-top: var(--space-md);
    }
    .gallery {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
      column-gap: var(--space-md);
      row-gap: var(--space-2xl);
      margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    }
    .piece {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-sm);
    }
    .piece-img {
      background: transparent;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .piece-img img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      transition: transform var(--dur) var(--ease);
    }
    .piece:hover .piece-img img { transform: scale(1.02); }
    .piece-meta {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: var(--w-base);
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-dark);
    }
    .piece-meta span { color: var(--text-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
    /* Each piece on its own row, varying widths/positions for editorial rhythm */
    .piece-1 { grid-column: 1 / span 8;  grid-row: 1; }
    .piece-2 { grid-column: 8 / span 5;  grid-row: 2; }
    .piece-3 { grid-column: 1 / -1;      grid-row: 3; }
    .piece-4 { grid-column: 2 / span 5;  grid-row: 4; }
    .piece-5 { grid-column: 7 / span 6;  grid-row: 5; }
    .piece-6 { grid-column: 5 / span 4;  grid-row: 6; }

    /* ---- FOTO GALERÍA ---- */
    .fotogaleria {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
      gap: 3px;
      background: var(--text-dark);
    }
    .fg {
      overflow: hidden;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .fg img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
      transition: transform 0.7s ease;
    }
    .fg:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }

    /* Posiciones en el grid */
    .fg-1 { grid-column: 1 / -1;   height: 58vh; }  /* textil-rosa — panorama */
    .fg-2 { grid-column: 1 / 5;    height: 52vh; }  /* silvia */
    .fg-3 { grid-column: 5 / 9;    height: 52vh; }  /* nopal-grana */
    .fg-4 { grid-column: 9 / 13;   height: 52vh; }  /* rodrigo */
    .fg-5 { grid-column: 1 / 8;    height: 50vh; }  /* tejedor */
    .fg-6 { grid-column: 8 / 13;   height: 50vh; }  /* figurines */
    .fg-7 { grid-column: 1 / -1;   height: 52vh; }  /* polvo-rojo — cierre */

    /* ---- RESPONSIVE ---- */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      /* float nav oculto en móvil */
      .float-nav { display: none; }

      /* HERO: font escala con viewport (en lugar de mínimo fijo 4.5rem=72px)
         17vw → ~64px en 375px, ~54px en 320px.
         "EL SECRETO" queda en ~103% del viewport = bleed mínimo legible.
         Tags reposicionados para no encimarse con las palabras. */
      .hero-word { font-size: clamp(2rem, 17vw, 14rem); }
      .hero-tag-tr { top: 108px; right: var(--space-md); }
      .hero-tag-bl { bottom: 108px; left: var(--space-md); }

      /* INTRO */
      .intro {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        min-height: auto;
        padding: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-xl);
      }
      .intro-blob img {
        max-height: 52vw;
        margin-left: 0;
        object-position: center;
      }
      .intro-content {
        padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-md) 0;
        gap: var(--space-lg);
      }
      .intro-secondary { align-self: auto; max-width: none; }

      /* PROYECTO */
      .proyecto {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        min-height: auto;
        padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-md);
        gap: var(--space-md);
      }
      .proyecto-title { font-size: clamp(3rem, 14vw, 7rem); }
      .proyecto-body {
        grid-column: 1;
        grid-row: auto;
        justify-self: start;
        margin-top: 0;
      }

      /* GRANA */
      .grana { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; }
      .grana-img { min-height: auto; grid-template-rows: 52vw 52vw; }
      .grana-img img:first-child { object-position: center 40%; }
      .grana-img img:last-child  { object-position: center 60%; }
      .grana-content { padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-md); }
      .cedula { grid-template-columns: 88px 1fr; }

      /* SISTEMA VISUAL */
      .sistema {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-md);
        gap: var(--space-xl) 0;
      }
      .sistema-body { grid-column: 1; margin-top: 0; }
      .module { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-md); }
      .paleta { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
      .tipos { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-lg); }
      .tipo { padding: var(--space-md) 0; }

      /* APLICACIONES */
      .aplicaciones {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-md);
        gap: var(--space-xl) 0;
      }
      .aplicaciones-body { grid-column: 1; margin-top: 0; }
      .gallery {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        row-gap: var(--space-xl);
      }
      .piece-1,
      .piece-2,
      .piece-3,
      .piece-4,
      .piece-5,
      .piece-6 {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
        grid-row: auto;
      }


      /* FOTO GALERÍA */
      .fg-1,
      .fg-2,
      .fg-3,
      .fg-4,
      .fg-5,
      .fg-6,
      .fg-7 {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
        height: 72vw;
      }
      .fg-1 { height: 56vw; }
      .fg-7 { height: 52vw; }

      /* BRIDGE */
      .bridge { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .bridge-text { padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-md); }
      .bridge-heading { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 9vw, 4rem); }
      .bridge-img { min-height: 56vw; order: -1; }
      .bridge-btns { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }

      /* FOOTER */
      footer {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
        gap: var(--space-lg);
        text-align: left;
      }
      .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: var(--space-sm); }
    }
    /* ---- LOADER ---- */
    #loader {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: var(--surface-cream);
      z-index: 9999;
      overflow: hidden;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .lw {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 9vw, 8.5rem);
      font-weight: var(--w-medium);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      line-height: 1;
      white-space: nowrap;
      will-change: transform, opacity;
      user-select: none;
    }
    @media (max-width: 767px) {
      .lw { font-size: 9vw; }
    }

    /* ---- LIGHTBOX ---- */
    #lightbox {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.96);
      z-index: 9998;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity 0.22s ease;
    }
    #lightbox.open {
      opacity: 1;
      pointer-events: all;
    }
    #lb-img {
      max-width: min(90vw, 1400px);
      max-height: 90vh;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
      user-select: none;
    }
    #lb-close {
      position: absolute;
      top: 1.2rem;
      right: 1.5rem;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      font-size: 2rem;
      line-height: 1;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 0.5rem;
      transition: color 0.15s;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
    }
    #lb-close:hover { color: #fff; }
    #lb-prev, #lb-next {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      background: none;
      border: none;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      line-height: 1;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      transition: color 0.15s;
      user-select: none;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
    }
    #lb-prev:hover, #lb-next:hover { color: #fff; }
    #lb-prev { left: 0; }
    #lb-next { right: 0; }
    .lb-open img { cursor: zoom-in; }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <!-- LIGHTBOX -->
  <div id="lightbox" aria-hidden="true" role="dialog" aria-modal="true">
    <button id="lb-close" aria-label="Cerrar">×</button>
    <button id="lb-prev"  aria-label="Anterior">‹</button>
    <img id="lb-img" src="" alt="" />
    <button id="lb-next"  aria-label="Siguiente">›</button>
  </div>

  <!-- LOADER -->
  <div id="loader" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="lw" id="lw-a">Descubre</span>
    <span class="lw" id="lw-b">El</span>
    <span class="lw" id="lw-c">Secreto</span>
  </div>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav class="nav" id="nav" aria-label="Principal">
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo" aria-label="Casa de la Grana - inicio">
      <img src="/images/logo-rojo.svg" alt="Casa de la Grana" />
    </a>
    <button class="nav-menu-btn" id="menu-toggle" aria-label="Abrir menú" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="menu-overlay">
      <span class="label">Menú</span>
      <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    </button>
  </nav>

  <!-- MENU OVERLAY -->
  <div class="menu-overlay" id="menu-overlay" aria-hidden="true">
    <ul class="menu-list">
      <li><a href="#visita" class="menu-item">Visítanos</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contacto" class="menu-item">Únete</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://nocheztlicalli.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="menu-item">Tienda</a></li>
      <li><a href="#legado" class="menu-item">Legado</a></li>
      <li><a href="#agenda" class="menu-item">Agenda</a></li>
      <li><a href="#exploradores" class="menu-item">Exploradores</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <img class="hero-bg" src="/images/img-01-hero.jpg" alt="" loading="eager" />
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-word hero-word-l">Descubre</span>
      <p class="hero-tag hero-tag-tr">Naturaleza, Historia, Cultura</p>
      <p class="hero-tag hero-tag-bl">Tradición, Arte, Preservación</p>
      <span class="hero-word hero-word-r">El Secreto</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- INTRO / BIENVENIDA -->
  <section class="intro">
    <div class="intro-blob" aria-hidden="true">
      <img src="/images/forma-grana.png" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="intro-content">
      <h2 class="intro-heading">Descubre<br/>el secreto</h2>
      <div class="intro-secondary">
        <p class="eyebrow">Junto a las guardianas del legado oaxaqueño</p>
        <p class="intro-body">Vive una experiencia inolvidable en Casa de la Grana, donde descubrirás el origen del rojo mexicano y otros colores ancestrales que forman parte del legado del México antiguo.</p>
        <a href="#contacto" class="btn btn-square">Visítanos</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EL PROYECTO -->
  <section class="proyecto">
    <p class="eyebrow proyecto-eyebrow">01 / El proyecto</p>
    <h2 class="proyecto-title">
      Nuestro<br/>
      pasado<br/>
      en la<br/>
      actualidad
    </h2>
    <div class="proyecto-body">
      <p>Casa de la Grana es un centro cultural en Santa Lucía del Camino, Oaxaca, dedicado a preservar el cultivo tradicional de la grana cochinilla y compartir su significado histórico.</p>
      <p>Un espacio donde el conocimiento científico se entrelaza con la experiencia creativa y la memoria comunitaria. Desde aquí rescatamos el legado de <em>Nocheztlicalli</em>, el insecto sagrado que tiñó imperios y continúa siendo fuente de vida y arte para la comunidad oaxaqueña.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LA GRANA / NOCHEZTLICALLI -->
  <section class="grana" id="legado">
    <div class="grana-img">
      <img src="/images/foto-yolanda.jpg" alt="Maestra Yolanda mostrando grana cochinilla en sus manos" loading="lazy" />
      <img src="/images/foto-nopaleras.jpg" alt="Nopaleras con grana cochinilla" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="grana-content">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow grana-eyebrow">02 / Nocheztlicalli</p>
        <h2 class="grana-title">El rojo<br/>que tiñó<br/>imperios</h2>
      </div>
      <dl class="cedula">
        <dt>Especie</dt>
        <dd><em>Dactylopius coccus</em></dd>
        <dt>Hábitat</dt>
        <dd>Nopal — <em>Opuntia ficus-indica</em></dd>
        <dt>Origen</dt>
        <dd>Mesoamérica, siglo XV</dd>
        <dt>Uso</dt>
        <dd>Tinte natural, pigmento carmesí</dd>
        <dt>Legado</dt>
        <dd>Patrimonio cultural mexicano</dd>
      </dl>
      <div class="grana-body">
        <p>La grana cochinilla es un insecto parásito del nopal que produce ácido carmínico, fuente del rojo más codiciado del mundo prehispánico. Mesoamérica lo cultivó por siglos antes de que España exportara el secreto a Europa, donde tiñó las vestiduras de papas, reyes y magistrados.</p>
        <p>En Oaxaca permanece viva la práctica del cultivo y la tintorería con grana, tejiéndose entre nopaleras, tinas y manos que la conservan generación tras generación.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SISTEMA VISUAL -->
  <section class="sistema" id="exploradores">
    <p class="eyebrow sistema-eyebrow">03 / Sistema visual</p>
    <h2 class="sistema-title">Gramática<br/>del rojo</h2>
    <p class="sistema-body">Una identidad construida desde la materia: el color de la grana, la huella de la mano que tiñe, la letra que ordena. Cada pieza del sistema visual responde al principio de cuidar el legado y dejarlo respirar.</p>

    <div class="module">
      <p class="module-label">Paleta</p>
      <div class="paleta">
        <div class="paleta-chip">
